Meet <b>Naruto</b> our featured citizen of the week!<br><br>Naruto has been living at <a href='/home/?user=narumaster'>92897-H Regal Mountain Drive</a> in Westridge since May 11, 2008. <br><br>Since the short time he moved here, Naruto has been enjoying the amazing views that Westridge offers of downtown Millsberry.<br><br>He is definitely a new comer to Millsberry, but during his short time in town, he's managed to rack up seven trophies. His honors include some of the most prestigious awards in Millsberry, like Kai's Surfari, Home Run Derby, and Sudoku. <br><br>Naruto describes himself as being very athletic, and it shows with his trophies for Rope Climb and Bumper boats.<br><br>When the weather's nice, you can hang out Naruto's back yard. He's got a hockey net, an igloo, a treasure chest, and a slide, so mixing it up shouldn't be a hard thing to do.<br><br>Next time you run into Naruto, shake his hand and thank him for being such a great citizen!<br></div>
